+------+----------------+
| id   | a              |
+------+----------------+
|    1 | [1,2,3,3]      |
|    2 | [5,6,7,7,NULL] |
|    3 | [5,6,7]        |
| NULL | NULL           |
| NULL | NULL           |
+------+----------------+
